\c 42
\s Bhuku 2
\p (Mapisarema 42 - 72 )
\s Chishuwo chomutapwa kushumira
\s Jehovha patemberi
\s Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; rwiyo rwe-
\s Mashiri rwavanakomana vaKora.
\p
\v 42
\v 1 Senondo inotakwairira hova dzemvura,
\s Saizvozvo mweya wangu unokutakwairirai imi Mwari.
\p
\v 2 Mweya wangu une nyota kuna Mwari,
\s iye Mwari mupenyu,
\s Ndichasvika riniko ndionekwe naMwari?
\p
\v 3 Misodzi yangu zvakanga zviri zvokudya zvangu
\s masikati nousiku,
\s Pakutaura kwavo zuva rose kwandiri vachiti,
\s "Mwari wako aripiko?"
\p
\v 4 Ndinorangarira zvinhu izvi, ndichidurura mweya wangu mukati mangu,
\s Zvokuti ndaienda navazhinji, ndichivatungamirira
\s kuimba yaMwari
\s Nezwi rokufara nokurumbidza, k*U.â€˜ Nalkkt NaktaxWn. xmt.zze(*.o
\p
\v 5 Unoshuwireiko, mweya wangu? Unoshaiwa rugare neiko mukati mangu?
\s Tarira kuna Mwari; nokuti ndichazomurumbidza hangu,
\s Nokuda kwokuponesa kwechiso chake.
\p
\v 6 Haiwa Mwari, mweya wangu
\s unoshuwa mukati mangu; Naizvozvo ndinokurangarirai ndiri
\s panyika yaJorodhani,
\s Napamakomo eHerimoni,
\s nechikomo cheM izari.
\p
\v 7 Pakadzika panodana pakadzika pakutinhira kwamapopopo enyu; Mafungu enyu namapoporodzi enyu akapfuura napamusoro pangu.
\p
\v 8 Asi Jehovha acharaira unyoro hwake
\s panguva yamasikati,
\s Usiku rwiyo rwake ruchava neni, Uye munyengetero kuna Mwari woupenyu hwangu.
\p
\v 9 Ndichati kuna Mwari, dombo rangu, "Makandikanganwireiko? Ndinofambireiko ndichichema
\s nemhaka
\s yokumanikidza kwomuvengi wangu?"
\p
\v 10 Zvakafanana nomunondo
\s pamapfupa angu,
\s kana vadzivisi vangu
\s vachindizvidza;
\s Kana vachiramba vachiti kwandiri, "Mwari wako aripiko?"
\p
\v 11 Unoshuwireiko, mweya wangu? Unoshaiwa rugare neiko mukati mangu?
\s Tarira kuna Mwari; nokuti ndichazomurumbidza hangu, Iye muponesi wechiso changu,
\s naMwari wangu.
\s Nokuda kwokuponesa kwechiso chake.
\p
\v 6 Haiwa Mwari, mweya wangu
\s unoshuwa mukati mangu; Naizvozvo ndinokurangarirai ndiri
\s panyika yaJorodhani,
\s Napamakomo eHerimoni,
\s nechikomo cheM izari.
\p
